			                                            	<strong>${comments.get(i).getText().substring(0, Math.min(comments.get(i).getText().length(), 20))}</strong> published <strong><fmt:formatDate value="${comments.get(i).getPubDate()}" pattern="yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss" /></strong>
